title: Bombers B-52
description: Karl Malden plays an air force sergeant who is tempted by a better-paying civilian job. Malden&#039;s daughter Natalie Wood is in love with a young colonel (Efrem Zimbalist Jr.) whom her father regards as an insolent hothead. The younger man proves his worth during jet maneuvers, while Malden decides that he&#039;s of more value in the service than as a working stiff.
